                </svg>
              </div>
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">24/7 Security Monitoring</h2>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
                Our Security Operations Center (SOC) never sleeps. We monitor your systems around the clock, 
                ensuring immediate response to any security incidents or suspicious activities.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
                <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
